						 <p>I think the tweaks definitely help - good stuff. Letter is still the big highlight. I remembered now what it reminds me of, the (excellent) videogame Sunless Sea (or Fallen London too), which tell their tales through evocative text in a similar way. It's really got the same mysterious, whimsical vibe in about a magical kingdom, love it!</p> 
